ُ - I swear)","transliteration":"falā","root":"","lemmaId":3147},{"id":"70:40:2","ayahNum":40,"wordNum":2,"word":"أُقْسِمُ","meaning":"I swear (negated by لَا before it)","transliteration":"uq'simu","root":"قسم","lemmaId":null},{"id":"70:40:3","ayahNum":40,"wordNum":3,"word":"بِرَبِّ","meaning":"by the lord (of ٱلْمَشٰرِقِ وَٱلْمَغٰرِبِ)","transliteration":"birabbi","root":"ربب","lemmaId":null},{"id":"70:40:4","ayahNum":40,"wordNum":4,"word":"ٱلْمَشٰرِقِ","meaning":"the places where the sun rises (connected to رَبِّ - Lord of)","transliteration":"l-mashāriqi","root":"شرق","lemmaId":null},{"id":"70:40:5","ayahNum":40,"wordNum":5,"word":"وَٱلْمَغٰرِبِ","meaning":"and the wests (possessed by رَبِّ)","transliteration":"wal-maghāribi","root":"غرب","lemmaId":null},{"id":"70:40:6","ayahNum":40,"wordNum":6,"word":"إِنَّا","meaning":"indeed we (subject of لَقٰدِرُونَ)","transliteration":"innā","root":"","lemmaId":502},{"id":"70:40:7","ayahNum":40,"wordNum":7,"word":"لَقَادِرُونَ","meaning":"surely We are capable/powerful","transliteration":"laqādirūna","root":"قدر","lemmaId":null},{"id":"70:41:1","ayahNum":41,"wordNum":1,"word":"عَلَىٰٓ","meaning":"upon/over (connected to نُّبَدِّلَ - we can exchange)","transliteration":"ʿalā","root":"","lemmaId":2582},{"id":"70:41:2","ayahNum":41,"wordNum":2,"word":"أَن","meaning":"that (introduces what is possible/able to happen with نُّبَدِّلَ)","transliteration":"an","root":"","lemmaId":368},{"id":"70:41:3","ayahNum":41,"wordNum":3,"word":"نُّبَدِّلَ","meaning":"we replace (connected to أَن that/to)","transliteration":"nubaddila","root":"بدل","lemmaId":null},{"id":"70:41:4","ayahNum":41,"wordNum":4,"word":"خَيْرًا","meaning":"better ones (object of نُّبَدِّلَ - we will replace)","transliteration":"khayran","root":"خير","lemmaId":null},{"id":"70:41:5","ayahNum":41,"wordNum":5,"word":"مِّنْهُمْ","meaning":"from them/than them (خَيْرًا - better than them)","transliteration":"min'hum","root":"","lemmaId":3464},{"id":"70:41:6","ayahNum":41,"w